summary:
My work consists of a system of discoveries through which I try to balance the structure of my philosophical belief.
Concepts that, in the hands of many, have become conventional, come into existence .
Thoughts that may be concerns, concerns, and questions of all, such as our origin and the substantial right to life.
My subjects are archetypal, timeless and yet so up-to-date.
I believe that human precense through art gives substance to the chaos of time and the man's visions as well as leading to catharsis and it is a guarantee of spiritual health.
